Jonathan Marks, is an independent media anthropologist, "insultant" and broadcaster. One of his projects is examining P2P technology for both production purposes (community radio in West Africa) as well as the next steps for wifi radios like those being produced by Reciva in the UK. This kind of techology is reaching a tipping point in the broadcast industry. His website is at [http://www.jonathanmarks.com www.jonathanmarks.com] .